Name: arlington_2004_zipcode_poly
Abstract:
This feature class consists of polygons representing ZIP Code areas in Arlington
    County. The United States Postal Service determines the boundaries, effectively
    showing delivery areas for each of the post offices serving the County. The
    boundary lines were determined using a national ZIP Code directory and internet
    resources provided by the USPS. It has not been authorized by the USPS, and
    should not construed as a legal document. This data is digitized and maintained
    by Arlington County for purposes of geographic analysis and mapping. Inquiries
    requiring “official” responses should be directed to the United States Postal
    Service.
